_sText:
Ive been playing some Hoejhus9 maps, and i decided to make my own that i would like. 
so i created this map. T has always had unfair advantage over CT with sniper on roof of T spawn. so now CT can get their revenge with their new sniper tower. Also added a "secret" walkway directly from bomb zone to T spawn. (look down!) and a not-so-secret sniper location, but to get there, its a secret.
It could properly be better, but i haven't mapped in a very long time..

Have fun !
